==== Translate ====
{{Msgbox
|id              = Msgbox:translate
|backgroundcolor = #faf6ed
|signal          = http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ee/Crystal_Clear_app_locale.png/48px-Crystal_Clear_app_locale.png
|heading         = This article needs to be ''translated''.
|message         = Please help improve the wiki by writing or translating the article into {{{1}}}.}}
 <nowiki>{{msgbox:translate|asdf}} <!-- where 'asdf' is the language it should be in --></nowiki>

